==International relations==

===Twin towns – sister cities===
Brăila is twinned with:
* Pleven in Bulgaria.
* Shumen in Bulgaria.
* Calais in France.
* Argostoli in Greece.
* Katerini in Greece.
* Bitola in North Macedonia.
* Kavadarci in North Macedonia.
* Denizli in Turkey.
* Nilüfer in Turkey.
* Beşiktaş in Turkey.

